Hi everyone!!


Make sure to download all the files for the website to work correctly.
As this is a back-end based website, make sure you have wamp or xampp installed on your system.

Database name = BlogWeb

Tables to create in phpmyadmin

1)posts
    post_id as PRIMARY KEY and AUTO INCREMENT
    post_title
    post_desc
    post_cat
2)blog_categories
    cat_id as PRIMARY KEY and AUTO INCREMENT
    cat_name 
  
  Note: Manually add as many categories as you want on your website in the table blog_categories
3)blog_posts_categories
    post_id FOREIGN KEY 
    cat_id FORIEGN KEY
    
After creating Database and all the 3 tables, you are good to go!! Thank you!!

Keep on Coding
